          </div>
          <div id="review_2508789_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2508789_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1402015">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1402015/" class="title-link">怎样从事公益事业</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1402015"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/robinsnow/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1096716-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/robinsnow/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">chenjie66</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-06-08"
      class="main-meta">2008-06-08 03:30:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1402015_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  怎么样，新年新气象，从nonfiction开始读哈   这本书前面有点没意思，但是越看越好看。主要讲的是一个美国登山者，在一次没有成功的征服世界第二高峰K2的探险活动中，迷了路，走进了一个纯朴贫穷的巴基斯坦的小村子里面。虽然村民们很穷，一年吃不上一次肉，还是拿出了家里最好...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1402015/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            Penguin Books2007版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1402015_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1402015_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





