  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/77306073/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u77306073-3.jpg" class="pil" alt="杨" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/77306073/">杨</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          2小时前          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:外国文学 纪实 旅行</span><br />

          <span class="">很感动.作者本是登山员,因村民救了他,为了回报村子,从在巴基斯坦,阿富汗等地区办学校的故事.让原本无法上学的孩子,特别是女孩都能受到教育.也让我从本书了解了一些穆斯林的生活.</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/98680377/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u98680377-12.jpg" class="pil" alt="食曼阿姨" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/98680377/">食曼阿姨</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          今天下午          想读      </div>

